### Test PDF Receipt Generation
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5135
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Generate Receipt PDF for existing order
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pdf/receipt/SO-20251105213131-5798
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Generate Receipt PDF for existing order (Arabic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pdf/receipt/SO-20251105213131-5798?language=ar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2a. Generate Receipt PDF with A4 paper
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pdf/receipt/SO-20251105213131-5798?paperType=A4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2b. Generate Receipt PDF with 80mm thermal printer
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pdf/receipt/SO-20251105213131-5798?paperType=Thermal80mm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2c. Generate Receipt PDF with 58mm thermal printer (Arabic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pdf/receipt/SO-20251105213131-5798?language=ar&paperType=Thermal58mm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

